                        <h3 align="left"><a name="adecrement"><FONT color="#156aab">c-jump facts:</FONT></a></h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                This game is not only about teaching and learning: it's fun and entertainment 
                                for the whole family!
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Skiing and snowboarding is a perfect programming analogy.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                c-jump game is ideal for home school education.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The game is based on the code of a real computer program!
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </font>
